message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with speech processing and recognition. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. cs.LG is another possibility as it deals with machine learning and neural networks. cs.SI is also possible as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. cs.CV is less likely as it deals with computer vision, but could still be a possibility if the paper includes visual information in addition to audio.
